sequenceDiagram
  participant Parent
  participant BankingApp
  participant YouthAccountAPI
  participant AccountService
  participant PaymentService
  participant TransactionService
  participant SettingsDB

  Parent->>BankingApp: Login & Select Youth Account
  BankingApp->>YouthAccountAPI: GET /api/youth-accounts/{id}/dashboard
  YouthAccountAPI->>AccountService: Fetch account details
  YouthAccountAPI->>TransactionService: Fetch recent transactions
  YouthAccountAPI->>SettingsDB: Fetch spending limit
  YouthAccountAPI-->>BankingApp: Dashboard data
  BankingApp-->>Parent: Show dashboard

  Parent->>BankingApp: Initiate Fund Transfer
  BankingApp->>YouthAccountAPI: POST /api/youth-accounts/{id}/fund-transfer
  YouthAccountAPI->>PaymentService: Initiate transfer
  YouthAccountAPI->>AccountService: Update balances
  YouthAccountAPI->>TransactionService: Log transaction
  YouthAccountAPI-->>BankingApp: Transfer result
  BankingApp-->>Parent: Show confirmation

  Parent->>BankingApp: Set Spending Limit
  BankingApp->>YouthAccountAPI: PUT /api/youth-accounts/{id}/spending-limit
  YouthAccountAPI->>SettingsDB: Update weekly limit
  YouthAccountAPI-->>BankingApp: Limit update status
  BankingApp-->>Parent: Show update confirmation

  Parent->>BankingApp: View Transactions
  BankingApp->>YouthAccountAPI: GET /api/youth-accounts/{id}/transactions
  YouthAccountAPI->>TransactionService: Query transaction history
  YouthAccountAPI-->>BankingApp: Transaction list
  BankingApp-->>Parent: Show history
